      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > Square Enix [5,419 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/square-enix">Square Enix</a> will release a demo for <em><a title="Games > Dragon Quest VII Reimagined [13 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/dragon-quest-vii-reimagined">Dragon Quest VII Reimagined</a></em> on January 7, the company announced.  <span id="more-1017914"></span></p><p>Save data from the demo can be carried over to the full game, and all users who play the demo will receive the “Day Off Dress” costume for Maribel for use in the full game.</p><p><em>Dragon Quest VII Reimagined</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,147 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,528 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [849 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,161 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,195 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2499860/DRAGON_QUEST_VII_Reimagined/" target="_blank">Steam</a> and <a href="https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/dragon-quest-vii-reimagined/9nkm0ckchdqx" target="_blank">Microsoft Store</a> on February 5, 2026 worldwide. Read more about the game <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/dragon-quest-vii-reimagined-announced-for-ps5-xbox-series-switch-2-switch-and-pc">here</a> <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/dragon-quest-vii-reimagined-details-visuals-story-features-characters-and-battle-system">here</a>, and <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/11/dragon-quest-vii-reimagined-details-adult-kiefer-storyline-stone-tablet-fragments">here</a>.</p><p>Watch the opening movie below.</p><h2><span>Opening Movie</